Live at the Hollywood Bowl is a live album by the American rock band The Doors. It was recorded on July 5, 1968 but not released until 1987; the full version of the concert was released on October 2012 also on LP. The video of the concert is available on DVD format on The Doors - 30 Years Commemorative Edition.
